quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  34,10,"Gom…óii Men okkii Daawuuda …ďural, immorde e Amen. [Men wi'i]: \"Ko onon pelle e colli, subbunhinodee e makko. Men newinani mo (tafugol) njamndi ndin"
  34,11,"(Men wi'ani mo wonnde): \"Gollu wutteeji njamndi, e…ď…ďaa ka tafoodi. Gollon golle mo∆ī∆īe, pellet, ko Mi Reenu…óo ko golloton kon"
  34,12,"(Men eltani kadi) Sulaymaana henndu ndun: dawol mayru ko yeru (yaadu) lewru, kirndol mayru kadi ko yeru (yaadu) lewu. Men honcinani mo …ďunndu sila (kire). Hino jinnaaji …óin, golliraynoo…ói yeeso makko, e duŇčayee Joomi Makko. Kala oo√Īiingii e majji, gaay e yamiroore Amen nden, Men mee…óina ngii lepte dul…ďoowe ngen"
  34,13,"Hi…ói gollana mo ko o faalaa: gila e tataaji, e nanndollaaji, e loo…óe wa'u…óe wa beeli, e payan…óe feŇčii…óe. \"Gollee, onon …ďeynguure Daawuuda, yetton (Alla)\", fan…óii e jeyaa…ďe Am …ďen, yettoowo (Lam)"
  34,14,"Nde Men √Īaawunoo e makko maayde nden, anndinaali …ói fii maayde makko nden, si wanaa gannguuji leydi(moo∆īu) …óin, hino √Īaama tuggordu makko ndun. Nde o fukkinoo, fee√Īani jinnaaji …óin, wonnde si …ói anndunoo ko wirnii, …ói √Īii…ďataano e lepte [jeyaagu] hoynooje"
  34,15,"Gom…óii wonaniino yim…ďe Saba'i …ďen e ko…óooli ma…ď…ďe …óin, maande; gese …ói…ói ka bannge √Īaamo e ka nano. (Men wi'ani …ďe): \"√Ďaamee e arsike Joomi mon, yetton Mo. Leydi ndin ko laa…ďundi, e Joomiraawo Haforoowo"
  34,16,"(Kono) …ďe …óuunii. Men wurti e ma…ď…ďe ndiyam waame, Men wa…ótitani …ďe gese ma…ď…ďe …óen …ói…ói, gese (goo) …ói…ói, mar…óe √Īaametee haa…óu…óo, e (le…ó…óe) du…ď…ďeeje, e huunde e jaa…ďe see…óaaje"
  34,17,"Ngool (yaggingol), Men yo…ďir…ďe ko …ďe yeddi kon. E hara Men yo…ďay si wanaa yeddu…ďe …ďen"
  34,18,"Men wa…ói hakkune ma…ď…ďe e ko…óooli …ói Men wa…ói barki e mun …óin, ko…óooli fee√Īondir…ói, Men e…ď…ďi e majji yaadu. (Men wi'ani …ďe): \"Yehee ton jemmaaji e √Īalormaaji, ko on hoolii…ďe"
  34,19,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Joomi amen, wo…ó…óindir hakkunde yaaduuji amen\", …ďe too√Īi ko'e ma…ď…ďe, Men wa…óti fillitee …ďe fii mun, Men senndindiri …ďe hattirde e senndirgol. Pellet, wonii e …óum, maandeeji wonannde kala heewu…óo mu√Īal, yettoowo (neema)"
  34,20,"Gom…óii Ibuliisa goonginii jikke mun …óen e ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe jokki mo, si wanaa fedde e gom…óim…ďe …ďen"
  34,21,"E doole alanaa mo e dow ma…ď…ďe, cemmbe (wurtugol), si wanaa tun, ko fii no Men anndira on gom…óin…óo laakara e on won…óo e sikke fii mun. Joomi maa non, e dow kala huunde, ko O reenu…óo"